MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2007-1630. Wolanin v. Holmes.

Cuyahoga App. No. 88454, 2007-Ohio-3410. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
